text: Marius Marro (born 16 December 1955) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
